Package uk.ac.leedsbeckett.oop

Class GameWorld.GameImages

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.leedsbeckett.oop.GameWorld.GameImages
Enclosing class:
GameWorld
public static class GameWorld.GameImages extends Object
A container class that holds all the images used in the simulation.

Instead of loading images all over the place, we load them once and store them all together in this container. Then we can pass this object around and any class that needs an image can get it from here.

This includes images for:

  • Grass background
  • Horizontal and vertical rail tracks
  • Crossing (where two tracks meet)
  • Locomotives facing each of the four directions
  • Carriages
